pgredis
=======

Requirements
------------
* PostgreSQL with PGXS
* Redis with CRedis (libcredis installed)


Installation
------------
Build pgredis from source and install it in your database by using the following commands:

1) make install
2) In psql: BEGIN; \i <path to pgredis.sql as shown in make install output>; COMMIT;


Feedback
--------
Please send bugreports and patches to <daniel@hobbit.se>.


